## Activity Entry Point

### MainActivity
- **File**: `app/src/main/kotlin/.../MainActivity.kt`
- **Purpose**: Single Activity hosting Compose NavHost
- **Lifecycle**: onCreate → setContent { SaviaApp { NavGraph() } }
- **Annotation**: @AndroidEntryPoint

## Deep Links (planned)

- `savia://chat/{sessionId}` → ChatScreen with session
- `savia://approval/{id}` → ApprovalsScreen with item
- `savia://capture` → CaptureScreen (quick capture intent)

## Testing Entry Points

- **Unit**: `app/src/test/kotlin/` (48 tests)
- **Integration**: `app/src/androidTest/kotlin/`
- **Run**: `./gradlew testDebugUnitTest`
- **Build+Test+Publish**: `./gradlew buildAndPublish`

## Known Issues (from CLAUDE.md)

- Chat timestamps: fixed (was showing UTC, now local)
- Bridge dedup: fixed (duplicate messages on reconnect)
- Session persistence: fixed (sessions survive app restart)
- CLAUDECODE env cleanup: fixed (env var leak between sessions)
- Project selector persistence: fixed (selected project survives rotation)
- APK version auto-increment: fixed (versionCode from git tag)
